Megan can't get on again. Time probs and stuff. Alot has been going on in her life lately. Anyways, I get to post with IR untill she can post again.

::IR/Prowl/Firearm/Cledar/Rixer/Forrior/Blyer::

IR looks over at Prowl as she hears his thought, nodding. -Yeah. Be careful, love.- she replies psychically to him, then looks back at all the other Maximals as Prowl leaves the room. The beams slowly begin to quicken around the target in the middle.

"Allright, Maximals. Are you ready?"
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Prowl walks out of the room and then jogs toward Firedrill, wondering where the bot was going.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Firearm, Cledar, Rixer, Forrior, and Blyer nod, getting into tenniss playing stances.
